A few hours later a cyclist received emergency medical treatment after being involved in an accident with a lorry in Camden, north London.

The London Ambulance Service said he was treated for a minor head injury and has been taken to St Mary's Hospital.

The death takes the number of to be killed in London to six in just 14 days.

